data.description: WOW factor alert! Check out this amazing multilevel in Lincolnshire Estates. Meticulously maintained is an understatement…completely updated kitchen, with painted cabinetry, quartz countertops, black SS appliances & coffee bar make entertaining so easy with an eat in kitchen & formal dining. Bathrooms are also updated with quartz. The laundry room (oh my!) makes everything a dream with stunning cork floors & organization that will be the envy of your friends! The main floor features bamboo floors, lots of fresh paint, the UL boasts new carpet in the family room, cozy fireplace and huge windows. The primary is a true oasis with gorgeous en suite & excellent storage. Two spacious bedrooms with superb closets and bathroom are on garden level. There is plenty of space to host family and friends in the gathering room with ample space for an office area. You will be delighted with the brand new high efficiency furnace. The fenced backyard with courtyard is ideal for entertaining.
